data.description: This 3 bed, 2.5 Bath home with a garage has amazing curb appeal on a corner lot. Step into the living room with hardwood floors and high vaulted ceiling.  The open-concept living and dining areas provide natural lighting and a great space for entertaining. Relax in front of the fireplace. Easy access to the backyard and deck.  The master bedroom is on the 1st main level with a bathtub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath on the upper level. Convenient to shopping and dining, minutes to downtown Simpsonville Arts Center, Heritage Park, Hospitals, and I-385.  Don't miss this one.  Schedule a tour today!
